New booking received

Hello <%= @owner.full_name %>,

You have received a new booking.

Business: <%= @business.name %>
Service: <%= @bookable_service.name %>
Customer: <%= @booking.customer_name %>
Phone: <%= @booking.customer_phone %>
Email: <%= @booking.customer_email.presence || "Not provided" %>
Start: <%= @booking.start_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") %>
End: <%= @booking.end_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M") %>
Status: <%= @booking.status.humanize %>

<% if @booking.notes.present? %>
Notes: <%= @booking.notes %>
<% end %>